The Supreme Council of Kenyan Muslims (Supkem) has welcomed the signing of an agreement that ended the blockade and boycott of Qatar by five of its neighbours, effectively ending the four-year gulf crisis.
Saudi Arabia and its regional allies reached a breakthrough agreement with Qatar on Tuesday not only ending the impasse but also restoring ties between the Arabian Gulf neighbours.



